Paper: hep-th/0003101

Date: 2000-03-13

Title: On the relevance of tachyons

Authors: J. A. Harvey, D. Kutasov, E. J. Martinec

Comments: 11 pages, harvmac; minor changes, references added

We study condensation of open string tachyons using renormalization groupflow in the worldsheet field theory. This approach leads to a simple picture ofthe physics of the nontrivial condensate.